{
  "texts": [
    "In the future, large multi-modal models will evolve toward integrated generation and understanding.",
    "Future large-scale models may also exhibit greater autonomous learning and exploration capabilities, actively acquiring, understanding, and using data from the physical world.",
    "3) Continuous learning and incremental learning.With the successful applications of large AI models in different fields and tasks, continuous learning [188] and incremental learning [189] will become important directions for development.",
    "Future large AI models may pay more attention to how to continuously learn and adapt in a constantly changing environment, and how to accumulate experience and knowledge in new tasks and domains.",
    "This requires models to have flexible learning capabilities to continuously update and optimize their performance using new data."
  ]
}